The Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, has announced the list of candidates for the forthcoming House of Representatives election in the state. PDP announced the list of nine candidates who emerged victorious at the just concluded primary election across federal constituencies in the state. The list below…. 1. Dr. Richard Gbande – Katsina-Ala, Ukum and Logo Federal Constituency 2. Hon. Terkaa Agba – Buruku Federal Constituency 3. Bob Tyough – Kwande / Ushongo 4. Rt. Hon. John Dyegh – Gboko/ Tarka 5. Mzondu Benjamin Bem – Makurdi / Guma 6. Comrade Ojotu Ojema – Apa/ Agatu Ado/ Okpokwu / Ogbadibo- Aida Nath 7. Emmanuel Ukaa – Gwer / Gwer West 8. Julius Atorough Tyough – Vandeikya / Konshisha 9. Alex Enokela (Ochacho Jnr) – Otukpo/ Ohimini.